HR NO. 139 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, Guy Williams is a true community leader and is most deserving of the
highest recognition for his outstanding efforts to assist Lakeview in the wake of Hurricane
Katrina.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Guy Williams, president of Gulf Coast Bank
& Trust, for his assistance to the Lakeview community in New Orleans following Hurricane
Katrina and does hereby extend sincere wishes that he remains prosperous in all of his
endeavors.
